}"},{"id":"2fc08a482800-3c053eb653e01124-0182","type":"action","label":"Outcome","designer":{"xLocation":733,"yLocation":3000,"next":"6c90788425bc-632f6c5ba608522b-608b"},"onInit":"// store the contents of the conversation
